      "writtenOn": "2019-06-12T21:12:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Let\u0027s rope in Jim, who owns the GrOvalOpFactory code.\n\nI think I would prefer a new entry point to do the circular checks and abort if not circular:\n\n  GrOvalRectOp::MakeCircularRRectOp\n\nThat way the second time we can just call GrOvalRectOp::MakeRRectOp, which won\u0027t do any circular checks.",
